(49, 3, NULL, 'California Garden Red Kidney Beans', 'Embark on a culinary journey with California Garden Red Kidney Beans, a pantry essential that adds a hearty and nutritious touch to your favorite recipes. Sourced from the fertile fields of California, these red kidney beans are a versatile and flavorful ingredient, perfect for creating wholesome and satisfying meals.', NULL, 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h43/h85/14786811887646/16671_main.jpg_480Wx480H', '<li><strong>Farm-Fresh Excellence:</strong> California Garden Red Kidney Beans are cultivated in the sun-drenched fields of California, ensuring a harvest of beans that are robust, flavorful, and rich in natural goodness.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Protein-Packed Nutrition:</strong> Packed with protein, fiber, and essential nutrients, these red kidney beans make a nutritious addition to your diet. Incorporate them into your meals for a satisfying and plant-based source of protein.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Conveniently Canned:</strong> Enjoy the convenience of canned red kidney beans that are ready to use in a variety of dishes. From chili to salads, stews to soups, these beans provide a quick and easy way to enhance the nutritional profile of your meals.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Versatile Culinary Uses:</strong> California Garden Red Kidney Beans are a versatile ingredient that complements a wide range of cuisines. Add them to Mexican dishes, pasta recipes, or create your own culinary masterpieces with these delicious and tender beans.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Quality You Can Trust:</strong> California Garden is committed to delivering quality products. Our red kidney beans undergo strict quality control measures to ensure they retain their natural flavor, texture, and nutritional value.</li>', 'California Garden', 'France', 19.95, 17, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-12-17 23:50:13', '1'),
(50, 2, '1234567890', 'Red Onions\n', 'Discover the bold and distinct flavor of red onions, a versatile ingredient that adds depth and color to a wide range of dishes. Known for their vibrant hue and pungent taste, red onions are a culinary essential for creating flavorful meals.', 'Red Fresh Onions', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h89/h34/35140081352734/480Wx480H_32762_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Superior Quality:</strong> Our red onions are carefully selected to ensure freshness, taste, and premium quality, sourced from trusted growers.</li>\n  <li><strong>Rich Flavor Profile:</strong> With a mildly sweet yet tangy taste, red onions are perfect for raw salads, pickling, grilling, sautéing, and adding a distinctive touch to various cuisines.</li>\n  <li><strong>Vibrant Color and Texture:</strong> Their deep red-purple layers not only impart a stunning visual appeal but also offer a delightful crispness and texture to dishes.</li>\n  <li><strong>Nutritional Benefits:</strong> Red onions are rich in antioxidants, flavonoids, and sulfur compounds, providing potential health benefits such as anti-inflammatory and immune-boosting properties.</li>\n  <li><strong>Storage Suggestions:</strong> Keep red onions in a cool, dry, and well-ventilated place, away from direct sunlight. Once cut, store them in an airtight container in the refrigerator.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 49.95, 25, 1, 30, 20, '50', 50, '10', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(51, 2, '2345678901', 'Tomatoes', 'Indulge in the vibrant taste of our farm-fresh tomatoes! Bursting with robust flavor and packed with essential nutrients, our tomatoes are the quintessential ingredient for countless savory dishes. From salads to sauces, soups to sandwiches, these juicy, plump tomatoes elevate every meal they touch.', 'Red Fresh Tomatoes', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h4d/h26/35140078174238/480Wx480H_32631_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Premium Quality Selection:</strong> Our tomatoes are handpicked from trusted farms, ensuring top-quality, ripe, and flavorful produce for your culinary adventures.</li>\n  <li><strong>Versatile Culinary Essential:</strong> Whether sliced, diced, roasted, or blended into sauces, tomatoes elevate the taste of pasta, pizzas, salads, sandwiches, soups, and countless other recipes.</li>\n  <li><strong>Rich in Nutrients:</strong> Tomatoes are a great source of vitamins A, C, and K, antioxidants like lycopene, and various minerals, contributing to overall health and well-being.</li>\n  <li><strong>Varietal Diversity:</strong> From cherry to beefsteak, heirloom to plum, explore a diverse range of tomato varieties, each offering its unique taste, texture, and culinary uses.</li>\n  <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store tomatoes at room temperature, away from direct sunlight, and use them within a few days to enjoy optimal freshness and flavor.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 12.95, 0, 0, 17, 80, '75', 125, '15', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(52, 2, '3456789012', 'Potatoes For Frying', 'Experience the crispy, golden perfection of frying potatoes - a kitchen staple loved for its versatility and comforting taste. Whether you\'re craving classic French fries, hash browns, or crispy wedges, our selection of frying potatoes promises the ideal texture and flavor for your favorite fried delights.', 'Potatoes for frying', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h8b/ha9/35140083679262/480Wx480H_157967_main.jpg', '<li>Premium Quality Selection: Our frying potatoes are carefully chosen for their ideal starch content and freshness, ensuring they deliver that perfect crispiness and fluffy interior when fried.</li>\n  <li>Versatile for Various Cuts: Ideal for slicing into thin fries, cutting into chunky wedges, or grating for hash browns, these potatoes maintain their texture and taste across different frying methods.</li>\n  <li>Superb Crispness: Their high starch content makes them perfect for achieving that coveted crispy exterior while preserving a tender inside, making them an excellent choice for frying.</li>\n  <li>Enhance Any Dish: Whether as a standalone snack or a side dish, frying potatoes are the foundation for creating delightful, indulgent treats suitable for any occasion.</li>\n  <li>Storage Suggestions: Keep potatoes in a cool, dark, and well-ventilated place, away from onions, to maintain their freshness. Avoid refrigeration, as it can negatively impact their texture when fried.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 27.95, 10, 0, 5, 51, '25', 25, '5', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(53, 2, '4567890123', 'Cucumber', '\nCucumbers are crisp, refreshing vegetables with a vibrant green skin. These elongated fruits have a mild, watery taste and a satisfying crunch. Packed with nutrients like vitamins K and C, cucumbers are low in calories and offer a hydrating, nutritious addition to salads, sandwiches, or simply enjoyed on their own as a healthy snack. They\'re a versatile kitchen staple, perfect for adding a fresh touch to countless recipes.', 'Cucumber', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h0d/h35/35140082335774/480Wx480H_32594_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Freshness Guaranteed:</strong> Our green peppers are sourced from top-quality farms to ensure freshness and superior taste.</li>     <li><strong>Versatile Ingredient:</strong> Add a crisp, sweet flavor to salads, stir-fries, fajitas, sandwiches, and more with these crunchy peppers.</li>     <li><strong>Nutrient Powerhouse:</strong> Packed with vitamins A and C, antioxidants, and fiber, green peppers contribute to a healthy, balanced diet.</li>     <li><strong>Colorful Options:</strong> Available in various sizes and shades of green, from vibrant lime to deep emerald, perfect for adding visual appeal to your meals.</li>     <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store these peppers in a cool, dry place or the refrigerator\'s crisper drawer to maintain their freshness.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 22.05, 0, 0, 17, 55, '100', 50, '20', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(54, 2, '5678901234', 'Carrot', 'Fresh, crisp, and bursting with natural sweetness, our premium carrots are nature\'s vibrant delight. Sourced from the finest farms, these carrots are packed with essential nutrients, making them a versatile and healthy addition to your meals. Whether used in salads, soups, stir-fries, or enjoyed raw as a wholesome snack, our carrots promise exceptional quality and taste. Discover the farm-fresh goodness that adds color and nutrition to your table with these crisp and flavorful carrots – a must-have staple for every kitchen', 'Carrot', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/he7/h1f/35140078338078/480Wx480H_32634_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Premium Quality:</strong> Our carrots are sourced from trusted farms, ensuring they are of the highest quality, fresh, and bursting with flavor.</li>\n    <li><strong>Versatile and Delicious:</strong> From salads to soups, stir-fries to snacks, carrots add a satisfying crunch and natural sweetness to a wide array of recipes.</li>\n    <li><strong>Nutrient-Rich:</strong> Packed with beta-carotene, fiber, vitamins, and antioxidants, carrots offer numerous health benefits, supporting eye health, immunity, and digestion.</li>\n    <li><strong>Assorted Varieties:</strong> Available in traditional orange, as well as heirloom varieties like purple, white, and yellow, offering an exciting array of colors and flavors.</li>\n    <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Keep carrots in the refrigerator to maintain their freshness and crispness. For prolonged storage, store them in a cool, dark place or in a container with slightly damp paper towels.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 17.95, 0, 0, 8, 81, '40', 40, '10', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(55, 2, '6789012345', 'Green Pepper', 'Discover the vibrant and versatile green pepper, an essential ingredient to elevate your culinary creations! Green peppers, also known as bell peppers or capsicum, offer a delightful burst of color, flavor, and nutrients to your dishes.', 'Short Desc 6', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h60/hde/35140076994590/480Wx480H_32652_main.jpg', ' <li>\n    <strong>Superior Quality Selection:</strong> Our green bell peppers are sourced from trusted farms, ensuring freshness, quality, and an exceptional taste that enhances your culinary creations.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <strong>Versatile Culinary Companion:</strong> Whether raw in salads, sautéed in stir-fries, stuffed for a flavorful main course, or grilled for a smoky twist, green bell peppers offer endless possibilities in various recipes.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <strong>Nutrient-Rich Profile:</strong> Packed with vitamins A and C, antioxidants, and dietary fiber, green bell peppers contribute to a healthy diet and support overall well-being.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <strong>Distinctive Flavor and Texture:</strong> With their mild, slightly bitter-sweet taste and satisfying crunch, these peppers add depth and color to an array of dishes, complementing other ingredients perfectly.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store green bell peppers in the refrigerator\'s crisper drawer, unwashed and placed in a perforated plastic bag, to retain their freshness and crispness for an extended period.\n  </li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 18.95, 0, 0, 12, 120, '60', 60, '15', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(56, 2, '7890123456', 'Zuchinni', 'Discover the mild, versatile charm of zucchini, a delightful summer squash that brings a delicate flavor and tender texture to various culinary creations. With its versatility and nutritional benefits, zucchini is a must-have vegetable that adds a subtle, yet distinct, touch to a wide range of dishes.', 'Short Desc 7', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h58/h15/35140078665758/480Wx480H_32609_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Premium Quality Selection:</strong> Our zucchinis are carefully picked at their peak ripeness, ensuring superior quality, freshness, and optimal taste for your culinary endeavors.</li>\n  <li><strong>Versatile Cooking Ingredient:</strong> Whether sliced into salads, grilled to perfection, sautéed in stir-fries, spiralized for pasta alternatives, or used in baked goods, zucchini adapts to various cooking methods effortlessly.</li>\n  <li><strong>Nutrient-Dense Superfood:</strong> Low in calories and rich in antioxidants, vitamins C and K, potassium, and dietary fiber, zucchini offers nutritional benefits that support a healthy lifestyle.</li>\n  <li><strong>Subtle Flavor and Tender Texture:</strong> With its mild, slightly sweet taste and tender flesh, zucchini effortlessly absorbs flavors while adding a pleasing texture to dishes.</li>\n  <li><strong>Storage Suggestions:</strong> Keep zucchinis in the refrigerator\'s crisper drawer, wrapped in a paper towel and placed in a perforated plastic bag, to maintain their freshness for an extended period.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 26.95, 0, 0, 6, 60, '30', 30, '10', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(57, 2, '8901234567', 'Big Eggplant', 'Experience the culinary versatility and rich flavor of big eggplants, a vegetable celebrated for its meaty texture and ability to absorb flavors. With their large size and robust taste, big eggplants serve as a canvas for creating a variety of hearty and delicious dishes.', 'Short Desc 8', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h47/ha5/35140080140318/480Wx480H_32606_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Premium Quality Selection:</strong> Handpicked at their peak for top-notch quality and freshness.</li>\n  <li><strong>Versatile Culinary Marvel:</strong> Ideal for grilling, roasting, sautéing, stuffing, or dips like baba ganoush.</li>\n  <li><strong>Meaty Texture and Rich Flavor:</strong> Known for a creamy, slightly bitter taste and substantial, meat-like texture.</li>\n  <li><strong>Nutrient-Rich Profile:</strong> Contains vitamins, minerals, antioxidants, and dietary fiber for a nutritious diet.</li>\n  <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Keep in the refrigerator\'s crisper drawer, unwashed and in a perforated plastic bag, for freshness.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 8.95, 0, 0, 20, 92, '90', 90, '25', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(58, 2, '9012345678', 'Yellow Bell Pepper', 'Embrace the vibrant, sunny hues and sweet, tangy flavor of yellow bell peppers, a delightful variety of bell peppers that elevate dishes with their distinct taste and vibrant color. These peppers are a culinary gem, offering both visual appeal and a delightful taste to a multitude of recipes.', 'Short Desc 9', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h48/h43/35140079157278/480Wx480H_32613_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Superior Quality Selection:</strong> Our yellow bell peppers are meticulously chosen for their freshness, superior quality, and exceptional taste, sourced from trusted farms to ensure premium produce for your culinary creations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Versatile Culinary Accent:</strong> Whether raw in salads for a pop of color, roasted for sweetness, grilled for smoky flavor, or sautéed in various dishes, yellow bell peppers add a sunny touch to an array of recipes.</li>\n  <li><strong>Nutrient-Rich Goodness:</strong> Loaded with vitamins A and C, antioxidants, and dietary fiber, yellow bell peppers contribute to a healthy diet while offering potential health benefits.</li>\n  <li><strong>Distinctive Flavor and Texture:</strong> With their mild, sweet taste and crisp, crunchy texture, yellow bell peppers bring a subtle sweetness and a satisfying crunch to dishes, enhancing their overall appeal.</li>\n  <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store yellow bell peppers in the refrigerator\'s crisper drawer, unwashed and in a perforated plastic bag, to retain their freshness and crispness for an extended period.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 15.99, 5, 0, 15, 41, '70', 70, '15', '1 Kg', '2023-09-20 00:00:00', '2023-09-22 05:55:23', '1'),
(59, 1, '3907837367', 'Navel Oranges', 'Indulge in the luscious, sweet-tart flavor and refreshing juiciness of navel oranges, a citrus delight celebrated for its vibrant taste and nutritional benefits. Known for their distinctive \"navel\" formation at the blossom end, these oranges offer a burst of sunshine in every bite.', NULL, 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/hd7/h4d/35140079484958/480Wx480H_32487_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Premium Quality:</strong> Our navel oranges are sourced from trusted orchards, ensuring freshness, superior quality, and exquisite taste.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Juicy and Flavorful:</strong> Known for their sweet, seedless, and easy-to-peel nature, navel oranges offer a burst of refreshing citrus flavor with each bite.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Nutrient-Rich:</strong> Rich in vitamin C, fiber, and antioxidants, navel oranges contribute to a healthy diet and support immune health.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Usage:</strong> Enjoy navel oranges as a wholesome snack, in fresh juices, salads, desserts, or as a zesty addition to various culinary creations.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Keep navel oranges at room temperature or refrigerate for longer shelf life. Store them in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 13.45, 0, 0, 8, 14, '100', 45, '20', '1 Kg', NULL, '2023-12-17 13:04:18', '1'),
(60, 1, '3256732567', 'Mandarin', 'Experience the delightful sweetness and easy-to-peel nature of mandarin oranges, a citrus gem known for its compact size, bright color, and refreshing taste. These small, seedless oranges are a popular choice for their convenience and juicy flavor.', 'Mandarin', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h6e/h3f/35140090789918/480Wx480H_32496_main.jpg', ' <li><strong>Premium Quality:</strong> Our mandarin oranges are carefully selected from trusted orchards, ensuring freshness, exceptional quality, and irresistible taste.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Sweet and Juicy:</strong> With their sweet and tangy flavor, mandarin oranges are bursting with refreshing citrus juice, making them a perfect on-the-go snack or addition to salads and desserts.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Easy-to-Peel:</strong> Known for their loose, easily separable skin, mandarins are effortless to peel, making them an excellent choice for kids and convenient snacking.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Nutrient-Rich:</strong> Rich in vitamin C, mandarin oranges provide antioxidants and fiber, supporting immune health and overall well-being.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store mandarin oranges in a cool, well-ventilated place or in the refrigerator to maintain freshness. Keep them away from moisture to prevent mold growth.</li>\r\n  </ul>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 13.95, 0, 0, 0, 0, '69', 59, '20', '1 Kg', '2023-12-17 17:13:03', '2023-12-17 13:13:03', '1'),
(61, 1, NULL, 'Imported Banana', 'Indulge in the tropical sweetness and creamy texture of imported bananas, a beloved fruit revered for its versatility, natural goodness, and delightful taste. These bananas are sourced from distant regions, offering a unique flavor profile and quality.', 'Imported Bananas', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h64/he6/35140084826142/480Wx480H_32567_main.jpg', ' <li><strong>Source:</strong> Our imported bananas come from select regions known for their premium-quality produce, ensuring freshness, taste, and texture.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Sweet and Creamy:</strong> With their rich, sweet flavor and creamy texture, imported bananas offer a tropical taste sensation that delights the palate.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Versatile Usage:</strong> Enjoy imported bananas as a healthy snack, in smoothies, baked goods, or as a natural sweetener in various culinary creations.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Rich in Nutrients:</strong> Bananas are a good source of potassium, vitamins C and B6, fiber, and antioxidants, contributing to a balanced diet and overall health.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store imported bananas at room temperature. Avoid refrigeration to prevent chilling injury, but if they ripen too quickly, consider refrigerating to extend their shelf life.</li>\r\n  </ul>', '', 'USA', 64.95, 10, 0, 20, 67, '80', 35, '20', '1 Kg', NULL, '2023-12-17 13:13:03', '1'),
(62, 1, NULL, 'Royal Gala Apples', 'Delight in the crispness and sweetness of Royal Gala Small Apples, a popular variety loved for its petite size, vibrant color, and exceptional taste. These apples are known for their unique flavor and suitability for snacking.', 'Red Apples', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h8b/haa/26615212605470/387719_main.jpg_480Wx480H', '<li><strong>Premium Quality Selection:</strong> Our Royal Gala Small Apples are carefully chosen for their freshness, superior quality, and exquisite taste, ensuring a delightful snacking experience.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Crunchy and Sweet:</strong> With their crisp texture and sweet, aromatic flavor, Royal Gala Small Apples offer a satisfying balance of sweetness and tartness.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Perfect Snack Size:</strong> These smaller-sized apples are ideal for on-the-go snacking, lunch boxes, or as a convenient portion for kids.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Versatile Usage:</strong> Enjoy Royal Gala Small Apples as a wholesome snack, sliced in salads, or used in baking delicious treats like pies and crisps.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store these apples in the refrigerator to maintain their freshness and crispness. Keep them away from other produce to prevent premature ripening.</li>', '', 'USA', 79.95, 8, 0, 98, 87, '56', 15, '20', '1 Kg', NULL, '2023-12-17 13:23:44', '1'),
(63, 1, NULL, 'Pomegranete', 'Discover the vibrant and tangy sweetness of pomegranates, a unique fruit prized for its jewel-like seeds and refreshing taste. Pomegranates are revered for their juicy arils and rich nutritional profile.', 'Pomegranate', 'https://cdnprod.mafretailproxy.com/sys-master-root/h19/h24/35140086300702/480Wx480H_397729_main.jpg', '<li><strong>Premium Quality Selection:</strong> Our pomegranates are carefully selected for their freshness, vibrant color, and plump, juicy arils, ensuring the best quality for your enjoyment.</li>     <li><strong>Juicy Arils:</strong> Pomegranates are known for their numerous edible seeds (arils) enclosed in a juicy, translucent pulp, offering a burst of sweet-tart flavor.</li>     <li><strong>Nutrient-Rich Superfood:</strong> Pomegranates are packed with antioxidants, vitamins C and K, fiber, and other beneficial plant compounds, offering various health benefits.</li>     <li><strong>Versatile Usage:</strong> Enjoy pomegranate arils as a refreshing snack, in salads, yogurt, smoothies, desserts, or as a flavorful garnish for various dishes.</li>     <li><strong>Storage Tips:</strong> Store whole pomegranates in the refrigerator to extend their shelf life. Once opened, store leftover arils in an airtight container in the fridge for a few days.</li>', 'Grocera', 'Egypt', 39.95, 0, 0, 0, 0, '52', 23, '15', '1 Kg', NULL, '2023-12-17 13:43:22', '1');

